data.description: Open House 1pm to 3pm this Saturday! Welcome Home to Spring Ridge! This expanded End Unit Townhome boasts Over 2400sq/ft and offers all of the builder's options, including full extensions on all 3 floors, a bathroom on all 3 floors, a bay window bump out, plus a deck! Enter on the lower "walk out basement" level, w/ hardwood floors, this level offers a powder room & coat closet, access to the attached, one-car garage, a study / office, Laundry & mechanical room closet, plus a Family Room / 4th Bedroom. The main level offers a 2nd convenient powder room, large formal room, Kitchen with 42" cabinets, center island, breakfast bar, and a Bay Window bump out for the breakfast nook, plus a Family Room with gas Log Fireplace and access to the elevated deck! The upper level boasts a large Primary Bedroom with Vaulted Ceiling, Full, Ensuite Bathroom with double sink vanity, large soaking tub and tiled shower, & a spacious walk-in closet; this level is rounded out with 2 more bedrooms and another Full Bath! Amazing location, walk to downtown Swedesboro, close to shopping and diners and easy commuting to anywhere - Route 295, NJ Turnpike, &  area bridges only minutes away! Sending to sought-after school districts in Swedesboro-Woolwich & Kinsgway Regional. Come see all that Swedebsoro has to offer!
